        <div class="space-y-2">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Custom Styling Showcase</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                Combine <code class="bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 rounded">Class</code>,
                <code class="bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 rounded">RowClass</code>,
                <code class="bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 rounded">CellClass</code>, and
                <code class="bg-muted px-1 py-0.5 rounded">HeaderClass</code> with Tailwind CSS
                utilities for full visual customization of the grid.
            </p>
        </div>

